Package org.fluentlenium.adapter.sharedwebdriver

Enum Class SharedWebDriverContainer

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SharedWebDriverContainer>
org.fluentlenium.adapter.sharedwebdriver.SharedWebDriverContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SharedWebDriverContainer>, Constable
public enum SharedWebDriverContainer extends Enum<SharedWebDriverContainer>
A singleton container for all running SharedWebDriver in the JVM.

It delegates all calls to a SharedWebdriverSingletonImpl instance.
